<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="investment-n">investment <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪn'vestmənt/    美 /ɪn'vestmənt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>投资：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The country needs <strong>investment in</strong> education.
这个国家需要对教育进行投资。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>投资额；投资的资产，（有用的）投资物：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a minimum investment of 1,000 yuan
1000元的最低投资额</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We bought the house <strong>as an investment</strong>(= to make money).
我们买了这所房子作为投资。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A little overlearning is usually a <strong>good investment</strong> toward the future.
一点点的过度学习通常是对未来的良好投资。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>（时间、精力的）投入</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The project demands considerable investment of time and effort.
该项目需要投入大量的时间和精力。</p></div></div>